PrecisAuthority (a) to make a nugatory payment to CAMMEX INC. in order to compensate them for loss of income and business due to the closing of their duty-free shop at the border crossing in EDMUNDSTON, New Brunswick, and (b) to lease some 558 square metres of land situate at the new border crossing to CAMMEX INC., for a term of five (5) years.
